Database - Class in org.usfirst.frc.team4950.robot
Over database that stores a snapshot of the joysticks and sensor values in a thread safe way This is constantly updated by multiple querying threads.
Database.ButtonName - Enum in org.usfirst.frc.team4950.robot
This is the enum that defines the different buttons that will be avaliable for use.
Database.Value - Enum in org.usfirst.frc.team4950.robot
an enum that describes all the sensors that this database is tracking.
This includes the joysticks.
To add a new sensor, add it here as an enum element and update the appropriate calling method.
disabledInit() - Method in class org.usfirst.frc.team4950.robot.Robot
This function is called once each time the robot enters Disabled mode.
disabledPeriodic() - Method in class org.usfirst.frc.team4950.robot.Robot
